WEBVTT

00:07:28.411 --> 00:07:31.703
But now, in the name
of urban renewal and progress,

00:07:31.727 --> 00:07:33.714
these communities are pushed out,

00:07:33.738 --> 00:07:36.332
in service of bringing them
into the 21st century.

00:07:36.904 --> 00:07:40.152
Professor Sharon Holland asked:

00:07:40.176 --> 00:07:43.843
What happens when a person
who exists in time

00:07:43.867 --> 00:07:47.294
meets someone who only occupies space?

00:07:48.897 --> 00:07:50.492
These racial struggles

00:07:50.516 --> 00:07:54.096
are battles over those
who are perceived to be space-takers

00:07:54.120 --> 00:07:57.041
and those who are perceived
to be world-makers.

00:07:58.041 --> 00:08:01.030
Those who control the flow
and thrust of history